    "rationale": "The UnitOfAssurance is structurally complete and the 13-factor credibility assessment has been performed in accordance with ASME V&V 40-2018 at Model Risk Level 5. Although all seven assessed factors show achieved levels below required levels and six factors remain unassessed, the assessment itself is accepted as a valid credibility evidence package documenting the known gaps. The package is accepted for submission to the regulatory dossier with the explicit understanding that the model is NOT accepted for its intended use pending resolution of all credibility gaps. NOTE: This package declares signatureAlg ed25519 and provides a hash but omits the signature field, leaving structural integrity unverifiable (W-SI-01).",
